reviewText: Everybody from Arkansas definitely should watch it! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
A truly interesting story and history of Fayetteville Arkansas. A must have for those who want to know more about Arkansas. Bill Clinton did a great job as narrator.

I am so proud to be from Fayetteville, Arkansas, and I am so proud of this film - this undertaking.  Now I have something to send my friends who live elsewhere when trying to explain this very special place and why I chose to move here 20 years ago without knowning anyone!  It is magical!
